> My toilet has started doing something weird. When I flush, the cap at the bottom of the basin behind the seat gets caught above the rod that's connected to the handle. So the only way to get the cap to go back down is the physically move over the rod so the cap can fall again. I don't know how this started happening or what to do about it.
